{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"16742ab108","title":"周恩来第一次接见内蒙四方面代表讲话纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a701822f91","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":10,"articleId":"16742ab108","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"肖华","id":"06af9ed14a","type":"人物"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"高锦明","id":"49002314ba","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"边境地区和少数民族","id":"c0cd6cf1d4","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"36159d0783","type":"title","text":"周恩来第一次接见内蒙四方面代表讲话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"edc50655e3","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：一九六七年二月十日下午五点五十分至七点五十分，地点：人民大会堂小会议室。接见人：总理、肖华。被接见人：内蒙古党委、内蒙古军区、呼市三司、红卫军四方面各五名代表。列席：刘华香（内蒙军区付司令员）。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de03768790","type":"paragraph","text":"（会议开始，总理一一询问了内蒙军区代表的姓名、成份、参军年限；问了内蒙古党委代表姓名、民族、在内蒙工作年限；问呼市三司代表姓名、年龄……）","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebbfe1144d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：谁叫高树华。（高树华站起来）你是师范学院的教师？哪里毕业的？","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91e06cdf55","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：师范学院。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca094c5753","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们三司有一个同学被打死，怎么不让检验尸体？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bba81d949c","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：因为他们要抢尸，毁灭罪证。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9bfd0798bb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是谁要抢尸？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2232b74346","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：红卫军。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a55a374fd3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么能抢尸体呢？为什么搞得这么对立？人是怎么打死的？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10d3fdde86","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：当时韩桐正在喊话，希望军区刘昌出来辩论。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f08887ec57","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：找刘昌辩论可以写封信嘛！用现在这个办法包围军区怎么能行呢？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c08aa1c614","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：正在这时，一个军官提着手枪跑出来，韩桐同志喊：同志们现在是用鲜血和生命保卫党中央、保卫毛主席的时候了。接着这个军官便开了枪，时间是二月五日中午12点15分。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"028c78c0f0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：韩桐是几年级学生？","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e44e090920","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：四年级学生。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a01a0a7739","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那里人？","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee8f235126","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：托县。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c027bb577a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那个盟？","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01180c5e4b","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：乌盟。到附属医院的时间是12点半。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af59bb377a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：当时人已经死了。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4dc89e1a6c","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：当时还没有死。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76dbca2c73","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：伤口在什么部位？","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7aeec1261","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：从左边第五根肋骨下打进去的，把肺动脉打穿，子弹还留在死者体内。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36405d7df2","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：我们当时已经拍了照，到医院以后，红卫军、革命战士的人包围了医院大门，要抢尸体。抢救了五个多小时，到五点五十分，当时给北京协和医院打电话，协和医院说：停氧20分钟已无法抢救。军区广播说，解放军不会开枪打革命学生。是“818”打的。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47aea98334","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：打的时候我不在，抢救时在。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ed1cbc4ae","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是你们的学生吗？","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"749dfd04c4","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：是的。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"422c75e29b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对军区）开枪打死人是怎么回事？","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09420e6062","type":"paragraph","text":"黄厚：我不了解这个情况，姜部长知道这个事情。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"58c005461b","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：那天十二点打死人，到了下午三点才听说。后来有个老工人反映说，他看见放了两个炮竹，还冒了一股烟……","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c067ea16fe","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：放炮竹怎么能打死人？他自己能把自己打死吗？你们检查枪膛子弹没有？","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a38e590a44","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：没有。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff4ee3c4c7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们没有检查枪膛子弹，怎么能断定不是你们打死的？你们这就输了一着嘛！如果我是个司令员，我马上就把人集合起来，检查枪膛子弹，你们没有做到这一点，你们追查凶手了没有？","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3c1558339","type":"paragraph","text":"黄厚：没有查出。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bbbaf572f7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们接到国务院、中央军委发的通知没有？","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a6634437b","type":"paragraph","text":"（打不还手，骂不还口，打伤了不开枪）","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74c8d03d9d","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：见到了。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"760c342c1e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：见到了你们为什么还这样做呢？我们都是军人嘛！我是个老军人，后来退伍，现在因为工作需要，又穿上了军装。打死人很容易查清，一清点武器，弹药，就清楚了嘛！","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c72f9a5ad2","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：我们当时没有验枪，这是我们的疏忽。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee7ac331f2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：静坐有多少人？","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a831aa205e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘文研：当时我在现场（接着揭发了姜文启的谎言）。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"268029ed6a","type":"paragraph","text":"黄厚：下午四点才广播枪打死了人。","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8da17983de","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你当时在现场吗？","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"947180bc7c","type":"paragraph","text":"黄厚：不在。","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ca659840e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（问姜）你在现场吗？","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c13c967590","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：不在。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e4eba971f","type":"paragraph","text":"敖长锁（军区代表）：我当时在现场。在迫不得已时发了三条通告，这个通告是在十一点多宣布的，我没有看到打倒的现象，要打倒，一定要哄起来冲击，在下午三点多钟才听到广播，因而军区没有检查枪支弹药。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1dfeff9b3d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这个问题先停止到这里，派人进一步调查。","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1798d122df","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：必须查清，交出凶手。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"18be4b0be8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：派谁都可以吗？","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43ee349ec1","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：只要总理派人去，我们就相信。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b208ee8744","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：中央派法医去检验，内务部去一个部长或付部长，带上个秘书和两名工作人员，乘飞机去。能不能夜航？（总理秘书立即打电话问能否夜航？回答说不能夜航。）那就明天拂晓起飞。","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ca3b150bd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们（指三司）负责人是哪位呀？","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9fcf9211f2","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：我，郝广德。","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a53d70333e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：飞机到了你们那边谁负责去机场接呀？","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4f5e2d573","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：薛贵元。","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fe721e951","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：军区谁去接呀？","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab32375cc6","type":"paragraph","text":"黄厚：杨明先，训练部部长。","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f6abcb8e8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：由军区去个吉普车去接。公安厅夺权了吗？","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0faca274a8","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：原来是造反派夺权，现在保皇派反夺过来了。","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f241c4f42a","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林（红卫军代表）：左派不是自封的。","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"24b884c7f0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：到底谁夺权，谁是保皇派，还要看看罗！红卫军方面要不要派人参加呀！（指验尸一事）","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8fdeaa0e7a","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我们不参加，因为这件事与我们没有直接关系。","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"744704a410","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：区党委要不要参加呀？","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ebaab40ab","type":"paragraph","text":"王铎：总理看，需要参加就参加，此事与我们没关系。","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a9da56f1e","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：你们支持三司冲军区，怎么没关系？","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b2c99e531e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：中央调查组、内蒙军区、呼市三司共同处理这件事，查清后将尸体火化，一定惩办凶手。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e71b97cc72","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：韩桐的弟弟在军区后勤部工作，他要求看尸体。","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7cd087462c","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：我们没有听到这个要求。","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ce4d00fc9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：死者的父、母、弟弟都可以参加验尸，把事实弄确实，如确实是枪伤，由政府负责抚恤。这个问题双方都不要再扩大宣传了，到中南海宣传很不象个样子，在北京在呼市都不要宣传了，查清后办案就是了。对待人民解放军要注意影响，不要丑化。你们（指三司代表）将来夺权还要靠解放军协助嘛！","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71140ed351","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理接着问了红卫军代表的姓名、职务）","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6876d82e63","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们（指红卫军）这个组织有多少人？怎么组成的？","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"358b1cb495","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我们是以工人为主体的群众组织，96%是工人、4%是干部。","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08dd6a095b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有转业军人吗？","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3dbbc75d6d","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：有很少，个别的。","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc8b2316a0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们谁负责的呀？","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71b702717c","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我负责。","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"050a565ca0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们有多少人？","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f1e94ca03","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：三万五千多人。","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d66d301577","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：光呼市吗？","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ab3f01001","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：光呼市。","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fcb7ebe7e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们橡胶厂有多少人？","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f61281439a","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：400多人。","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e0a28316a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：总指挥部谁负责呀？","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8bd3771301","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：暂时也是我负责。","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4326ff8d9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：一共有多少人？","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"912b016bf1","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：二十二万人，其中红卫军三万多人。","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1002332be3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这个数字有出入吧！","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02a125fb17","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：还有小学生。","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85b10717cc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这不可能，呼市一共有多少人呀？","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1097ee07c","type":"paragraph","text":"王铎：不连郊区农民，有三十多万。","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d35b4a7501","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：共三十多万，你们就有二十二万，这样一算，平均一家要有两、三个参加了。北京几百万人，能组织起来的最多有一百万。","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db2323bea5","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我们统计数字有出入。","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4388077966","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不是数字有出入的问题，你们以少报多，这不够实事求是，不符合毛泽东思想。你们（指三司）有多少个组织？","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"38d217815d","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：65个组织。","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f31fe6f4f2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：学校几个？","index":95,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8954bba86","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：大专院校六个、中专16个。","index":96,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1aa6ab5448","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们工农兵革命委员会有多少人？怎么组成的？","index":97,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf68978035","type":"paragraph","text":"樊俊智：共有四万多人，主要是农民，有六千多转业军人。","index":98,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"851721e42d","type":"paragraph","text":"刘文研：一开始，他们是全国荣复军，他们成立的是全国性的，我们有充分资料可以说明这个问题。他们在去年十一月已经组织起来啦，有宣言、有纲领。他们的传单说是总理同意的，借着总理的名义，便大规模地发展起来了，他们在农村，十三岁以上的都发展了。","index":99,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2093c3396","type":"paragraph","text":"樊俊智：我们是12月30日成立的工农兵革命委员会，总理接见我们回去以后，就宣布第一个宣言作废。既然要摆，就摆一摆吧！不要说组织的名称，主要看组织的行动，摆摆么！有理不在言高，山高遮不住太阳，我们现在全国连个点也没有，和别的组织没有联系。","index":100,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d3eaf7d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们把转业军人组织在一起，这我去年十二月份有个讲话，已经讲了应该逐步取消。应该按照产业、职业、行业来组织革命组织，不能把人从各方面抽出来，单独组成全国、全省区性的组织，因为这样组织就成了一政党了。我们经常学习毛主席语录：“领导我们事业的核心力量是中国共产党。”只有按照产业、职业、行来、一个厂子、一个系统组织在一起，才能统一起来。存在决定意识嘛。你们这个组织各行各业都有，应该逐步取消，我劝你们逐步取消。因为不按产业、职业、行业组织、容易被坏人利用。有些组织是毛主席和林副主席下令取消的。有些组织，如：荣复转业军人、一九六五年大专院校毕业实习生、临时工、合同工、半工半读、学徒工，一九六一、一九六二年下放干部、下乡知识青年、支边青年等等，有的要回上海，要回来搞全国组织，我也不同意，结果这些人就流来流去，甚至流到部里，最后被我们查出来了，共有七、八种，查也查不清。有些已经查清了，如：“红旗军”，有个黄老，工农兵有两个头子，是大流氓，这些组织是被反动头子利用的。第一次查出“红色职工造反总部”，后来，又查出个“荣复军”，湖南长沙又查出了“红卫军”等等，不论那一派，都要注意不能跨越产业、职业、行业来组织，这容易被坏人利用。","index":101,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ca82ec3b8","type":"paragraph","text":"刘文研：现在他们这个组织与包头、全国有联系，第二个宣言仍说以荣复转退军人为主，北京有个“黄老”他们有个“潘老”，他们领导人白振玉、郑福田说是总理同意搞的。","index":102,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"affa5b380c","type":"paragraph","text":"樊俊智：白振玉不假，领导成员有四个，总理说不允许，12月28日发的宣言，有这么一句话不假。工人、农民大部分都在我们组织里，我们最近准备清理组织。看一看我们工农兵成立后砸了哪个组织，有哪些牛鬼蛇神，三司砸了那些组织，有哪些牛鬼蛇神，我们跟全国连一个联络站也没有，我们也可以把三司的成员摆摆。","index":103,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d4df76172","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不要谈这些了（总理点郭长俊的名）。","index":104,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93206df900","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：郭长俊没来，我替他，我是学习调度员的，五九年石家庄毕业，我原是铁路职工红卫兵，铁路局有个红色造反团三千人，铁路系统共六千人，呼市五千人，呼铁一千，在家的九百二十人左右，最近夺权是我们夺权。","index":105,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30f167177c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：人家不是已经夺了吗？","index":106,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f2bf5b50b","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：他们是假夺权，那派局处领导人就有46人。","index":107,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc45bf35aa","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是不是军队帮你们夺的？","index":108,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6947ab187b","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：我们是八日早五点夺权，部队在那儿有一个警卫班，因为他们要抢枪支弹药，部队下午六点才去的。我们夺权后他们不上班，我们就发扬穷棒子精神，自己干，我们有准备，我们夺权的那一天生产任务完成的最好。","index":109,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a462ce2bd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：局机关同意你们观点的有多少人？","index":110,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12448fa29f","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：200多人。","index":111,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5dcf7497ef","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是否发生过堵塞现象？","index":112,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"284b1d8649","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：暂时还没有。","index":113,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa6b1bc7f3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们夺权是否有外援。","index":114,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcac094102","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：有，因为我们是少数派，需要大联合支援，是无产阶级联合总部支援的。","index":115,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fda909f9f6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们“无产者”有多少人？怎么组成的？","index":116,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46ef5fb7db","type":"paragraph","text":"张启生：共有两万多人，机关干部两千，大中（专）院校学生一万二千，手工业工人四千，郊区农民三千。","index":117,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bd7cec521","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那你们就是极大的多数派了，你们几个组织有交叉，学生很多，你们的代表都是工人，干部。为什么没有学生。我建议你们找个学生代表，看看你们的学生属于哪一派？","index":118,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de9b0ca76b","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：清华井冈山驻呼联络站的同志参与了这件事情，应该有代表参加。","index":119,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8298dd1974","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：可以参加一个人（后决定宁奎喜参加）。高锦明同志放出来没有？你们（对区党委代表）还叫高锦明来吗？","index":120,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0c222c491","type":"paragraph","text":"郭以青：高锦明同志是我们首席代表，要叫他来。","index":121,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ede8f570ed","type":"paragraph","text":"姜文启：如果让高锦明来，王逸伦也应该来。","index":122,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a40d88b65f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们几个方面有什么意见？","index":123,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79f126b9c8","type":"paragraph","text":"郭以青等：我们同意让高锦明同王逸伦一起来。","index":124,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f15b93ae9","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：我们也同意。","index":125,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19120fc8a5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那就明天一起来，都不要带秘书了，区党委派一个工作人员来就行了。（三司代表递上“818”和军区红色造反团给总理的信，总理看了后问黄厚）你们那里还有造反派？怎么没有他们的代表？是不是怕他们？","index":126,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a275427ee","type":"paragraph","text":"黄厚：我们不怕。（最后决定让红色造反团派一名代表一一王建荣来）","index":127,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7b68e3aaed","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我们也应该增加代表？","index":128,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b4693e07f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不谈了，不谈了，如果需要增加代表，以后再考虑，先搞打死人的问题，今天就谈到这里。","index":129,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"16742ab108","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}